data.description: *SELLER OFFERING $3,300 CREDIT FOR RATE BUY DOWN* Welcome to 2332 Kismet Court, a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom townhouse nestled in the heart of South Kalispell. This well-maintained gem offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Step inside and be greeted by the welcoming open floor plan that boasts a modern look and feel. The living area flows seamlessly into the well-appointed kitchen, complete with a large pantry with sliding barn door, an island with barstool seating, and a generous amount of counter space. This inviting space is perfect for entertaining and spending quality time with loved ones. The three bedrooms offer restful retreats after a long day. The master suite features a private bathroom, while the additional two bedrooms share a second full bath. Step outside and enjoy the charming front porch overlooking the cul-de-sac. Conveniently located just minutes away from Highway 93 Bypass access, schools, dining, and amenities!
